# The store picks a backend automatically:
#
# 1) Redis (required on Vercel / serverless). Set EITHER pair — Vercel's Storage
#    tab injects the KV_* pair for you when you add a Redis/Upstash store:
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
#   ...or...
# KV_REST_API_URL=
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
#
# 2) JSON file (LAN / single always-on host) — used when no Redis vars are set.
#    Optional: where to write it. Defaults to .data/pads.json in the cwd.
# PAD_DATA_FILE=
